Package fr.cnrs.iees.properties.impl

Class ReadOnlyPropertyListImpl

java.lang.Object
fr.cnrs.iees.properties.impl.ReadOnlyPropertyListImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
PropertyListGetters, ReadOnlyPropertyList, fr.ens.biologie.generic.DataContainer, fr.ens.biologie.generic.Sizeable, fr.ens.biologie.generic.Textable, Cloneable
Direct Known Subclasses:
SimplePropertyListImpl
public class ReadOnlyPropertyListImpl extends Object implements ReadOnlyPropertyList, fr.ens.biologie.generic.Textable
A read-only property list - property values can only be set at construction time. Internally, the container is a sorted map so that property keys always come in the same order.
Author:
Jacques Gignoux - 29 janv. 2019
